[normal]The N
[normal]ational Oceanography Centre N
[normal]OC 
[normal]www.noc.ac.uk
[normal] 
[normal]is wholly owned by the N
[normal]atural Environment Research Council N
[normal]ERC 
[normal]and is 
[normal]the UK’s leading institution for sea level science, coastal and deep ocean research and technology development. 
[normal]NOC
[normal] works in close partnership with institutions across 
[normal]the UK and international marine science community, providing National Capability such as hosting the Royal Research Ship Fleet, a range of world-leading autonomous underwater vehicles, the National Marine Equipment Pool, National Oceanographic Library, British Oceanographic Data Centre and specialist staff and laboratory facilities.
